The Office of the Chief Justice has on Thursday warned the public to ignore a fake SMS that is circulating instructing people to appear before the High Court, particularly in the KwaZulu Natal Province. The Office of the Chief Justice said the High Court does not issue SMSes with notices for court appearances. It said people should ignored the fake sms. An example of the SMS is shown below: “You are to appear before the high court on07/12/17. Please view the case documents on
http://court14.96.lt/case77213 for more information. Kind Regards” -TNA Reporter